  A([💡 Spark: ROY insight]):::spark
  B[Define the claim\nWords → Structure → Understanding]:::think
  C{Is this diagram\nhonest — not happy-path?}:::gate
  D[Add loopbacks,\nforks, dead ends]:::revise
  E{ROY check:\nDid the words earn the visual?}:::gate
  F[Reframe in prose —\ndiagram isn't carrying its weight]:::revise
  G[Council of AIs:\nSame brief, independent models]:::think
  H{Does disagreement\nreveal structure?}:::gate
  I[Adjudicate + synthesize\nacross council outputs]:::think
  J[Ship: Post + Article v0.1\nProtoform release]:::ship
  K([🔧 Replit: Convert to\na runnable tool]):::tool

  A --> B --> C
  C -- Still lying --> D --> C
  C -- Honest --> E
  E -- Poor ROY --> F --> B
  E -- Strong ROY --> G --> H
  H -- Just noise --> G
  H -- Structure found --> I --> J --> K